                        <interp inst="t18731027-name-45" type="given" value="FRANCIS"></interp>FRANCIS CAVERLY</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City Policeman</hi> 145). The prisoner was given into my custody by the last witness on Tuesday, 14th October, about 1.30—I took him to the station.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I never had his watch, if I had it the policeman must have seen me give it to somebody.</p>
